headline: Elastic: Despite The Strong Gen AI Opportunity, I'd Rather Go With MongoDB
summary: Elastic is well-positioned in search, but AI competition from Datadog and MongoDB looms. Learn why ESTC stock is a hold and offers less potential than peers.
